---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About – Shreya V Holla"
  description="Learn more about Shreya V Holla – designer & developer focused on thoughtful, minimal digital products."
>
  <section class="section" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
    <div class="container stack-lg">
      <header>
        <p class="hero-kicker">About</p>
        <h1 id="about-heading" class="section-heading">Behind the portfolio</h1>
        <p class="section-subtext">
          This is placeholder copy about Shreya. Swap it with your story: how you
          think about design, why you build the way you do, and what you value in
          collaborations.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="stack-lg">
          <div class="surface">
            <p>
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed vel
              porttitor nunc. Vivamus posuere justo mauris, quis facilisis lorem
              vehicula eu. Phasellus hendrerit nisl id dolor dignissim, vitae
              tristique sem tempor.
            </p>
            <p>
              Integer posuere, sapien a ultrices volutpat, nibh leo molestie
              sapien, vitae lacinia sem felis vel mauris. Donec ac urna a arcu
              finibus consectetur. Donec ultricies augue sed sapien mattis,
              gravida aliquam erat malesuada.
            </p>
            <p>
              Use this section to talk about what lights you up: thoughtful
              typography, systems thinking, collaboration, or anything else that
              feels like you.
            </p>
          </div>

          <section aria-labelledby="skills-heading">
            <h2 id="skills-heading" class="section-heading" style="font-size: 1.4rem;">
              Skills &amp; focus
            </h2>
            <p class="section-subtext">
              A quick snapshot of the spaces you like to work in.
            </p>

            <div class="tag-list" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
              <span class="tag">Product design</span>
              <span class="tag">Interface design</span>
              <span class="tag">Design systems</span>
              <span class="tag">Frontend development</span>
              <span class="tag">Prototyping</span>
              <span class="tag">Accessibility-minded</span>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>

        <aside aria-label="Portrait placeholder">
          <div class="about-photo" role="img" aria-label="Placeholder portrait area">
            <div class="about-photo-label">
              Future photo of Shreya lives here.
            </div>
          </div>

          <section
            aria-labelledby="availability-heading"
            style="margin-top: 1.8rem;"
          >
            <h2 id="availability-heading" class="section-heading" style="font-size: 1.2rem;">
              Currently open to
            </h2>
            <ul style="margin: 0.8rem 0 0; padding-left: 1.1rem; font-size: 0.95rem;">
              <li>Thoughtful product teams and studios</li>
              <li>Independent client collaborations</li>
              <li>Speaking, teaching, and mentoring</li>
            </ul>

            <div style="margin-top: 1.4rem;">
              <Button href="mailto:hello@example.com">Start a conversation</Button>
            </div>
          </section>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

